race.comment: OVER DRAFT (8) is a progressive type who scored a strong on speed win on the Sunshine Coast last time at this trip. Drawn for the run of the race and can go on with it. JIMMYINTHEJUNGLE (3) was tested in tougher company at the end of last campaign but did resume here last time and absolutely bolted in. Fitter for two trials and expected to be on song. GO MARO (7) also resumes and is fitter for one trial. Has the ability and will be running on hard late.  RUSSIAN DIVA  (5) returns from a break. Has won fresh and presents on the back of a one trial. Goes well this course and placed only try course and distance.
